issue.title: "Error #5507: Circuit simulation submission limit reached" when submitting final Solution to Tunnel Circuit

content.raw:
Here are some updates:

1. Teams can submit up to 10 simultaneous runs.
2. Vinayak Kankanwadi, you hit a corner case that we didn't anticipate. You had 10 runs going, and then submitted to the Tunnel Circuit. This caused the system to reject your Tunnel Circuit submission. I'll follow up with you through your email on subt-help.
3. If you see "Admin Review", then please contact us either on this issue tracker or via subt-help@googlegroups.com
